<h2>About</h2>
<p class=first>In June 2010, <span class=bigger>Virtuoso's Philharmonic School of Music</span> was opened in Vellore, Tamil Nadu <a style=text-decoration:underline;font-size:1.3em;color:#06f href=contact.html#map>(find us).</a>
Virtuoso's is a one stop studio for all your music education needs and is
committed to offering music access to everyone.
</p>
<p>We offer a full schedule of <span class=bigger>private lessons, group classes and workshops</span> in a variety of
music disciplines. Classes are designed to enrich the music education and to unlock the
creative potential of the student. Both the experienced artist and enthusiastic novice
will find exciting opportunities at Virtuoso's School of Music.
</p>
<p>We are fully equipped with state of the art teaching materials and facilities. A <span class=bigger>jamming room</span> is available, where students can practise their instruments individually or play together as a group.</p>
<p>We welcome you to contact us and join our family of talented individuals, eager students and appreciators of the fine arts.
</p>
<h2>Founder</h2>
<p>VPSM is led by its founder H.Lieutenant P. Subramani L.M.M.E.(Retired). An Army musician officer with a collective experience of over 32 years in military music wing. During his service in the Indian army he served  as the conductor of The Madras Regiment Military Band and lead numerous parades in different parts of the country. He also served as instructor at the Military Music College, Pachmarhi. Post retirement he served as the principal of Police Training College - Music Wing, Avadi. </p>
</div>
